data.title: Trip to Maranello
data.text:
#TripToMaranello Ferrari Scuderia Praha

TRIP TO MARANELLO to celebrate the 25th anniversary of #Ferrari in the Czech Republic was literally a dream ride.

25 years of Ferrari representation in the Czech Republic is a very important moment for us this year. Such a significant anniversary calls for a significant celebration. And how best to celebrate these successful 25 years? Well, with you!

A total of 25 cars set off on a 4-day drive to Maranello. A city that turns the boyhood dreams of many enthusiasts into reality.

25 Ferrari cars

1,300 km driven

50 Ferrari enthusiasts

4 countries

4 days on the road
